Since you are still encountering errors, I will provide all the necessary `ALTER TABLE` statements again, with clear instructions to run them **one by one** and **verify success** after each. This is crucial.

Please execute the following SQL statements in your Supabase SQL editor. For each statement, wait for confirmation of success before proceeding to the next. If you encounter any error, please stop and report it to me immediately.

```sql
